 incident captured since the vote was announced. It only took 2 minutes to bare witness to a Racist with a flag on the outside of his car starts trying to push in front of the queue for petrol. He see's Muslim Cab driver and starts shouting 'Your an Arabic cunt\\\" over and over. Cabbie starts following him out telling him to go away. The guy gets out of his car and offers to attack him if he gets out of his car. All of this happens in front of a busy petrol station with other Black and Asian drivers filling up. \\r\\n\\r\\nWe cannot allow people to stand alone when attacked like this. We must always act and protect those who are vulnerable. In numbers we have strength. In acting we show practical solidarity. There's no doubt that the Muslim driver on the end of this racist incident will be feeling isolated, angry and upset. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe EU referendum has emboldened people exactly like this. It has given the confidence for racists to gloat in public and infused then with a sense of national pride which they use as a weapon to attack anyone they see as not 'english'. We can only expect that these racist incidents that occur so soon after the Referendum will be a regular occurrence, even in London were there is a higher percentage of Remain voters and more unity among communities.\\r\\n\\r\\nReg Plate - : VX56 UVW. 2006. Silver Vauxhall Insignia.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nAll this In Harrow, London\\r\\n\\r\\nLink to Video https://www.facebook.com/LondonBlackRevs/videos/848333021965937/\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"HA2 9DL\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"London Black Revolutionaries\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-01T11:54:20.302Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-01T12:36:45.578Z\",\"support\":null,\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported