":null},{\"id\":150,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"date\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Cable Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Lancaster \",\"description\":\"At a stoplight, just before the car pulled away, some men shouted out the car's window at a woman, 'Hey Palestinian Princess, go on home!' The woman looked like she was of Middle Eastern descent, but was around university student age and was dressed in a similar manner to the other (white) students that were walking in her group with her.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"LA1 1HH\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Lancashire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Morgwn\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T09:19:30.152Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T09:45:38.003Z\",\"support\":\"The woman was walking in a group, so I heard her friends ask her if she was OK and say some about what a***holes those men were and one of the guys said the men were obviously cowards since they drove off so fast. I was satisfied that she was at least being comforted by her group of friends with her.\\r\\n\\r\\nI had just walked past this group, so I only heard the abuse start and turned around as I saw the guys calling abuse start to laugh before they quickly drove away. I therefore didn't get a licence plate number. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":153,\"lat\":\"51.494205\",\"lng\":\"-0.116125\",\"date\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Juxon Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I was in my garden, picking raspberries. There is a low wall between my garden and the estate's comunal garden. A couple of women were sitting on a bench watching their dogs. When they were about to leave one of them turned and saw me, and called me a \\\"dirty bitch\\\" out of the blue and walked off. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"SE11 6NH\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T10:10:00.387Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:04:43.432Z\",\"support\":\"No one else was around, apart from her friend who laughed. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":173,\"lat\":\"52.636878\",\"lng\":\"-1.139759\",\"date\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Leicester\",\"description\":\"ADT Cabs in Leicester City - Driver refused to pick up owner with his guide dog - clearly breaking the law and discriminatory \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Leicester\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:54:22.642Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:54:22.642Z\",\"support\":\"Only the owner https://www.facebook.com/jessica.amy.g/videos/636291893217728/\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":177,\"lat\":\"50.340378\",\"lng\":\"-4.783425\",\"date\":\"2016-06-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Saint Austell\",\"description\":\"In work was told by a person that there are too many immigrants in the country and they had voted out because of it. They stated they were proud to be a racist.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Cornwall\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:03:25.746Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:46:21.856Z\",\"support\":\"I told them I was a migrant and it was people like me that they were voting out. I was helping a family member of theirs at the time. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":180,\"lat\":\"51.79929\",\"lng\":\"-0.201873\",\"date\":\"2016-07-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Welwyn Garden City\",\"description\":\"Both my children were told to \\\"go home, and leave this country\\\" by a woman on a bus as they travelled home from school. My children are of a mixed heritage, mother is from Kenya and I am also of mixed heritage of English and Kashmir, but both kids are UK citizens born in London and Hertfordshire and have always lived here.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Hertfordshire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:15:02.530Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:17:50.116Z\",\"support\":\"No one offered them any support, with several other adult passengers laughing at them and pointing.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":151,\"lat\":\"52.2257\",\"lng\":\"-2.742772\",\"date\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Leominster\",\"description\":\"Two days after the referendum (Saturday) my husband was walking alone through a small park in Leominster on his way to the train station from work at about 7.30pm.  A group of lads at the skate park shouted at him: 'Go home black bastard', 'he's a paki', 'he's a nigger', 'we're in control now'.  He walked faster as he was out-numbered and afraid.  The incident has been reported to the police, who came round to our house two days later and took a statement and said the local team would be taking it up.  The very helpful officer thought there would be little chance of a conviction for hate crime unless there had been witnesses or CCTV.  \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Herefordshire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T09:27:58.506Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T09:44:59.788Z\",\"support\":\"There was no-one else close enough to the incident to hear what was going on.  My husband's work colleagues are supportive.  Some of them are Polish and are very worried for their security. The police have been very supportive, and one of the local county councillors has written a letter to the local newspaper condemning racism wholeheartedly.  We have had no reply from our MP Jesse Norman.  \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":152,\"lat\":\"51.477796\",\"lng\":\"-3.177594\",\"date\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Saint Mary Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Cardiff\",\"description\":\"Boys in a bar told me \\\"you look a bit European, when are you fucking off back to Europe\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Cardiff\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"H\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T10:05:47.183Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:04:16.523Z\",\"support\":\"No one but they were kicked out of the bar shortly after this for being loud\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":155,\"lat\":\"51.781858\",\"lng\":\"-2.576528\",\"date\":\"2016-07-03T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Forest of Dean District\",\"description\":\"This morning my neighbour after a diatribe of anti europe stuff said \\\"we can't even deport the rapist muslims, these muslims are taking our jobs, Syria is where I want to go because it's empty now, they are all coming here and taking what's ours\\\" \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Gloucestershire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T10:42:41.997Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:05:47.049Z\",\"support\":\"\\r\\nI spoke up against scapegoating and tried to explain it in a calm way\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":156,\"lat\":\"53.36063\",\"lng\":\"-1.470657\",\"date\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Well Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Sheffield\",\"description\":\"Asian lady complaining that teenage girl who had run into a pub, clearly hiding, had been throwing stones at her house.  Large group of men shouting back harassing the lady \\\"We're all Brexit aren't we\\\", and \\\"how did you vote, love?\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"S8 9TZ\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"South Yorkshire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T10:47:40.654Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:06:40.786Z\",\"support\":\"Pub staff offered support to the lady\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":167,\"lat\":\"51.497495\",\"lng\":\"-0.135658\",\"date\":\"2016-06-23T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"City of Westminster\",\"description\":\"Don't take this the wrong way, please. I am one of those people they call an 'ex-pat', living on my old age pension in France. Britain just had a referendum but I was not allowed to vote because I have been living here over 15 years. I can only assume that was because I am now regarded as friends with those naughty foreign French people, even though the results of that referendum now threaten my very survival since I suffer from a long term illness which requires regular medical treatment and there is a danger of my medical cover being withdrawn if the UK does exit. My partner is a Swiss lady so she would then be unable to come with me to the UK because of restrictions on 'immigration'. She will be 76, and I will be 72  this month. I accuse a certain N.Farage of racism in this case.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T13:17:36.373Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T13:17:36.373Z\",\"support\":\"Even the British high court refused to help me and others in similar situations.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":168,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"date\":\"2016-06-29T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"23 Queen Square\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"A patient in an NHS hospital refused to be seen by a consultant co