but otherwise silent until...\\r\\n\\r\\n...just before the Wapping Health Center bus stop, older white guy bursts out with \\\"FUCKING HELL! Speak English...\\\" (first part REALLY loud, second part nearly under his breath). Startled, I looked up to see him looking our direction, and clearly ask in my American accent, \\\"Is there a problem, sir?\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"No problem. *surprised look which quickly narrows into a squint* Why would you ask that?\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"Well, most folks who don't have a problem don't suddenly burst out with obscenity, or make comments about the language others are speaking in.\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"I don't have a problem. And even if I did, that's my business, innit? Mind your own business!\\\" and he fled off the bus to avoid further confrontation.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:05:53.143Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:07:26.021Z\",\"support\":\"I spoke up and confronted the bigot. He left to avoid further verbal confrontation. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":159,\"lat\":\"55.857245\",\"lng\":\"-4.255306\",\"date\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Glasgow\",\"description\":\"My brother and I were walking by the bank machines outside the st enoch bank of scotland around 4pm on friday the 1st of july when suddenly two neds lunged at a mixed race man next to us.They called him a p*** and said he should go home as well as attempting to hit him with a bottle.My brother stepped in and made sure the guy was safe but the two guys went further down past the subway station and pointed/stared down other POC that walked by.We are both a quarter turkish and frightened that our dede(grandpa) could be harassed like this.Post-Brexit Britain is not somewhere I'm happy to live in.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Glasgow City\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Jessica Secmezsoy-Urquhart\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T12:01:25.342Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:45:01.104Z\",\"support\":\"My brother did but most people didnt which surprised me.My brother like me is autistic so I was scared the guys would maybe lash at him too but I was proud he did step in when no one else was doing so.We both told POC walking towards where they were to avoid them/stay safe.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":171,\"lat\":\"53.480759\",\"lng\":\"-2.242631\",\"date\":\"2014-08-17T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Manchester\",\"description\":\"A Labour councillor Mark Hackett called me all sorts of racist and Islamophobic names in emails and made all sorts of mad accusations based on his interpretation of the spelling of my name and me helping Stop The War organize an event.  Manchester City Council found him guilty of breaking \\\"code of conduct\\\" but allowed him to retire without take any action.  Ms Liz Treacy the legal head of Manchester City Council refused to take my phone calls when I was being harassed.  Liz Treacy has now dragged out a supposed potential hearing for over two years and allowed Mark Hackett to walk away quietly.  Incidentally Stop The War Manchester staff did not offer me any help to try and get justice. And more than 2 years on I am still trying to get justice - the racist Manchester Police force has ignored this and indeed their Salford East GMP has harassed me when I made other complaints of anti-social behaviour that was taking place in the area.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater Manchester\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Adnan Q\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:41:50.108Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:41:50.108Z\",\"support\":\"No one helped me but Islamic Human Rights Commission put a school leaver on the case and tried to take undue credit. Other organizations have also tried to take credit for him \\\"retiring\\\" and I find this so pessimistic - that there is a victim and the so called advocacy groups are either ignoring me or trying to falsely take credit for absolutely nothing.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":158,\"lat\":\"54.971994\",\"lng\":\"-1.616569\",\"date\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Clayton Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Newcastle upon Tyne\",\"description\":\"A group of drunk men were chanting \\\"He's not English, she's not English\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"NE1 5PW\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Tyne and Wear\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T11:58:38.637Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:44:37.607Z\",\"support\":\"None.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":178,\"lat\":\"52.75168\",\"lng\":\"0.402296\",\"date\":\"2016-06-28T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"King's Lynn and West Norfolk District\",\"description\":\"So for the first time in a long while I experienced a narrow minded racist in town this morning. Who told me now we've had the referendum all the immigrants should go home. To which I ignored at first till he followed me continuing to say it and tell me to go back to my own country with everyone starting to look and watch. To then get so angry and turn and shout at him that he's a narrow minded self obsessed little person with no idea of democracy and what voting out of the EU actually meant. I shouted at him that he should read the history books and actually find out some facts before shouting his mouth off in public just because he sees a foreigner. I angrily continued to shout that I was born and brought up here and this is my country as much as anyone else's who works and pays taxes and owns property. To then get claps from everyone watching the situation along with a community police officer. I've never been so angry, but also so proud to have actually done that out in the open and in front of so many people.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Norfolk\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:22:08.156Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:46:10.516Z\",\"support\":\"I spoke up\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":175,\"lat\":\"51.081397\",\"lng\":\"1.169456\",\"date\":\"2016-06-20T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Shepway District\",\"description\":\"Man on bus talking loudly about Brexit, while making it clear that he loves people of all creeds and colours, in a 'some of my best friends are black' kind of patronising manner. Then starts talking about the whinging Scottish and how they don't know when to shut up. Young girl who has been quietly listening to all this, answers her mobile phone, and it is clear she is Scottish. Scottish girl then challenges the anti-Scottish man who then denies he said anything. But he did.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Kent\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T15:28:33.219Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:47:10.049Z\",\"support\":\"No. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":174,\"lat\":\"51.428289\",\"lng\":\"-0.102429\",\"date\":\"2016-07-03T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Knights Hill\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Lambeth\",\"description\":\"Black British woman and white English man, shouting out racists comments near bus stop in West Norwood. Shouting that Europeans should go home directly in front of me and my family who are mixed family of Europeans and British. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"SE27 0HY\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T15:25:16.444Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:47:23.899Z\",\"support\":\"No one said a word\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":172,\"lat\":\"50.834209\",\"lng\":\"-0.271556\",\"date\":\"2016-06-17T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Weald Dyke \",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Shoreham by Sea    Adur District\",\"description\":\"a cruel,  highly racist entire row of home-made posters in a UKIP supporters front garden, abutting the street so it could not not be seen by anyone passing by to and from the beach. I spoke to several folk who were very upset.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"bn \",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Sussex\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T14:49:56.655Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:48:20.144Z\",\"support\":\" Someone put a polite but firm notice on top of one of the posters saying how appallingly racist they were and how ashamed it made people here feel.\\r\\nIt was reported to the police.\\r\\nThey were all removed from the garden. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":280,\"lat\":\"55.975117\",\"lng\":\"-3.166243\",\"date\":\"2016-07-09T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Edinburgh\",\"description\":\"Neo- Nazi stickers(National Action) found in Leith Edinburgh Scotland.\\r\\nscrapped them off.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Edinburgh\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-17T08:56:53.207Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-18T08:57:27.294Z\",\"support\":\"No.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":164,\"lat\":\"51.513162\",\"lng\":\"-0.088338\",\"date\":\"2016-06-13T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"On the westbound Central Line in London on the 13th June around 6pm my friends and I were travelling towards Soho for the Orlando vigil. A woman of colour was stood next to us. An elderly white man asked her if the train went to Holborn. When the woman said \\\"Pardon?\\\" as she had not heard him, he repeated it slowly, loudly, and patronisingly as if to make the point that she couldn't speak English. He continued to harass her. When a friend of mine asked him if he would like to sit down to get him away from the woman, he directed his rant towards us (visibly members of the LGBT community) shouting amongst other things about how we were \\\"riffraff\\\" and ought to be \\\"burnt\\\".\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T12:55:34.760Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T16:51:53.485Z\",\"support\":\"When the woman was being harassed, I offered her my seat (to get her away from the man) and my friend offered the man a seat for the same reason. When he turned his attentions to us, no-one did anything.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":179,\"lat\":\"51.60197\",\"lng\":\"-0.05391\",\"date\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I have been told to fuck off from this country by a black man\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N17\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Yuksel Ozkaya\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:00:33.468Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:18:17.243Z\",\"support\":\"\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":181,\"lat\":\"51.605984\",\"lng\":\"0.057462\",\"date\":\"2016-06-23T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Chigwell road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Redbridge\",\"description\":\"Racist abuse last 3yrs from  next door neighbour. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"Ig88bl\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Rashid\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:22:29.636Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:24:31.783Z\",\"support\":\"No \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":182,\"lat\":\"54.540308\",\"lng\":\"-1.293636\",\"date\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Westbury street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Thornaby\",\"description\":\"I am a PhD student at Durham University, Queens Campus, Stockton-on-Tees. I am an international student from India. I currently live in Thornaby. \\r\\nOn Saturday 2nd July  2016 at 8:30am, I went out to buy milk from nearby Saiinsbury's (Westbury street). While heading home, I felt a heavy and painful punch on my back. I must have stopped breathing for few seconds and when I turned around, there was well-built drunk man staring at me angrily. He asked me about my birth place but I couldn't speak. He then told me that \\\"What the f*ck are you doing here...Go back to your country\\\". I was shaking and confused as this was the first I encountered a physical violence. He then crossed the street and went inside one of the back alleys. I kept walking home and started sobbing. I felt like my birth was a big mistake and I shouldn't exist according to the theory of natural selection.\\r\\nIt's been 6 and a half years, I never encountered such an incident personally. I dedicated my whole University life in the UK and being a self-funded student I have enormous pressure to achieve my academic goals.\\r\\nThis incident happened on Westbury street, Thornaby, nearby the Sainsbury's. And my house is few blocks away from where it happened. \\r\\nThe man was probably 6' tall, broad shouldered and shaved head.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"TS17 6NE\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Stockton-on-Tees\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Mohit Jain\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:40:43.039Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T18:44:27.039Z\",\"support\":\"There was an old couple standing at the bus stop nearby who saw the whole incident. They made sure I was okay after the man crossed the street (which was really nice of them).\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":184,\"lat\":\"53.683298\",\"lng\":\"-1.505924\",\"date\":\"2016-06-28T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Batley Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Wakefield District\",\"description\":\"First a man leaned out of his car, made an obscene gesture and told me to f*** off. Then 15 minutes later a man told me to 'Get back where I came from'\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Yorkshire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T19:30:42.681Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T19:32:02.181Z\",\"support\":\"Nobody spoke up or offered support\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":186,\"lat\":\"51.561145\",\"lng\":\"-0.108864\",\"date\":\"2016-06-29T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Isledon Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"My partner (he's 64 and white British) told me this: he was at a bus stop on the way to a hospital appointment. Another white man aged about 50, and drinking cider, was also there. A black woman aged about 65 came out of the nearby doctor's surgery and sat at the bus stop. The cider drinker leaned over and called the woman an f***ing black c***.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N7 7JP\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-03T22:19:44.072Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-03T22:34:13.798Z\",\"support\":\"My partner told the man he was being racist and threatened to call the police. The man stopped and my partner \\u0026 the woman got on their bus.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":188,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"date\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Kings Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Brighton\",\"description\":\"I was cycling westwards on Brighton sea-front cycle lane at slower than walking speed to allow an oncoming runner and cyclist pass safely.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe white male runner passing me in the opposite direction deliberately jabbed his elbow hard into my upper arm. He didn't speak or look at me before or after the incident.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"BN2 3AF\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"East Sussex\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T09:47:05.596Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T10:11:57.247Z\",\"support\":\"\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":189,\"lat\":\"51.548156\",\"lng\":\"-0.075671