auls Avenue (in front of Sainbury's crossing)\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I needed to stop my car suddenly as the red light came up and waited a pedestrian that was crossing the street... My red light was still on but some people not really happy of me waiting started shouting and I tried to reply: _I'm waiting the green light and then came\\r\\n-FUCKING IMMIGRANT...\\r\\n\\r\\nI was so shocked that I couldn't remember to take note of his plate\\r\\n\\r\\nThat happened in Willesden Green High Street x St Pauls Avenue (in front of Sainbury's crossing)\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"NW2 BRENT\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"BRENT\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Julia Penido\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T11:42:55.221Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T12:40:44.898Z\",\"support\":\"nope\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":194,\"lat\":\"56.116523\",\"lng\":\"-3.936903\",\"date\":\"2016-06-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Various\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Stirling\",\"description\":\"I have received several comments about being English (in Scotland). \\r\\n\\r\\nPeople chanting at me in a pub to \\\"fuck off home\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\nSomeone threw a beer can at me in a park on another occasion\\r\\n\\r\\nOn a third occasion my car was vandalised\\r\\n\\r\\nOn a fourth, well before Brexit, there was graffiti daubed on my front door\\r\\n\\r\\nI have only put the date of the first one as it doesn't allow you to put more than one date.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"FK7 7JZ\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Stirling\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T16:04:40.027Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T16:04:40.027Z\",\"support\":\"No\