7.721Z\",\"support\":\"I was shocked - happened to fast to say anything to them. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":193,\"lat\":\"51.604967\",\"lng\":\"-0.072279\",\"date\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Scotland Green\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Haringey\",\"description\":\"I have been finding Islamophobic stickers on lamp posts and street signs all around Hartington Park in Tottenham, and up and down streets in the surrounding area. Most of them are in English, some of them are in Polish. When I see them I scrape them off, and over the last three month I have must scraped off at least thirty or forty, and that's just in a very small area. Just today I found a bunch of new ones that read \\\"FUCK ISLAM\\\" in huge letters, and in small letters \\\"Stop the Islamisation of Europe\\\" and \\\"Europe Wake Up\\\". Keep an eye out for this in your area, as most people don't think to look at lamp posts.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N17\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-04T15:55:51.765Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-04T16:25:48.896Z\",\"support\":\"Most people don't know these stickers are even there. A few of them have already been half scraped off so you know some people are seeing them. I use a dog-tag to scrape them off, so carry something similar if you want to battle this  racist propaganda.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":195,\"lat\":\"52.539611\",\"lng\":\"-0.263173\",\"date\":\"2016-06-29T