orted_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":210,\"lat\":\"53.54093\",\"lng\":\"-2.111366\",\"date\":\"2016-07-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Oldham District\",\"description\":\"I was out shopping with my wife and a white middle aged man approached me an wife and said \\\"we don't want you paki muslim here fuck off to your own country\\\". I was shocked and stunned by the comments. I didn't say anything in response because I didn't know what else he might do. This was deeply upsetting and has meant that we are now more cautious about what time we go shopping. What upsetted me the most was the fact that i was born here.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater Manchester\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T10:21:25.227Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:50:17.292Z\",\"support\":\"No one said anything. People were just looking and staring. Not a single person challenged his behaviour. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":212,\"lat\":\"51.590428\",\"lng\":\"-0.102759\",\"date\":\"2016-05-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Westbury Avenue\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"My wife and I are in a mixed-race relationship (white and Anglo-Caribbean), early 30s. On May 5th 2016 we were walking into Turnpike Lane station at midday when we heard a man shouting. We turned to see a well dressed white man in his mid-40s, obviously inebriated, shouting unintelligibly at a black woman at the bus stop. He noticed us and said \\\"its bad enough all these niggers here, but when you see a white man betraying his race, like this bossman and his nigger bitch . . .\\\" whereupon he stopped talking as I had one hand around his throat. I was dragged away by my wife before I could strike the man, but as we left he continued his tirade against us, following to the entrance of the station but not following us inside.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N15 3NX\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:04:26.753Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:51:05.642Z\",\"support\":\"No. There was a crowd of at least 30 people within ear shot, evenly spilt white and black, but no one said anything or intervened, although all looked shocked.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":213,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"date\":\"2016-07-08T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Burton upon trent\",\"description\":\"'This is England' someone muttered in the charity shop while I was chatting in French to my mum. To be honest I completely dismissed it as a stupid person's comment and didn't even register it until I got out.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T13:14:42.127Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T13:53:04.255Z\",\"support\":\"\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":215,\"lat\":\"50.461921\",\"lng\":\"-3.525315\",\"date\":\"2016-07-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Torquay\",\"description\":\"\\\"EU Rats. Go Home Now\\\". Graffiti on side of Health Centre in Torqu