eported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":252,\"lat\":\"52.56909\",\"lng\":\"0.838587\",\"date\":\"2016-07-06T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Griston Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Thetford\",\"description\":\"A long worded, laminated sign has been put up in the bus stop on the corner of Griston Road.\\r\\nIt reads; 'Piss off home EU scum. We don't want your grubby berry picking paws dragging round here, ruining our beautiful English land with your swan eating.'\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"IP25 6DN\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Norfolk\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-06T22:04:31.817Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-06T22:54:03.598Z\",\"support\":\"No. It is a sign. But still hasn't been taken down.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":254,\"lat\":\"51.756808\",\"lng\":\"-1.251779\",\"date\":\"2014-10-08T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Mansfield Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Oxford\",\"description\":\"While I was walking down the street, a man on a bicycle slowed down as he passed by, and shouted 'terrorist!' at me before speeding away. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Oxfordshire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-07T00:50:10.648Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-07T08:33:02.149Z\",\"support\":\"There was nobody around at that particular stretch of the street. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":255,\"lat\":\"51.745469\",\"lng\":\"-1.230752\",\"date\":\"2016-01-20T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Cowley Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Oxford\",\"description\":\"A man yelled 'ISIS' at me as he walked past. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Oxfordshire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-07T00:51:22.662Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-07T08:33:20.618Z\",\"support\":\"No. But I brandished my umbrella at him threateningly as I asked him what he said. He did not respond. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":256,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"date\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Newcastle \",\"description\":\"Im a mixed race Swiss.\\r\\nI was in Newcastle for work the other day. Spoke on my phone in french a bit in a cafe and got sideways glances from some girls.\\r\\nThey started to very loudly talk about how n words should all go back to Africa and how they were annoyed given the brexit vote that they hadn't all been sent away yet. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-07T09:37:31.157Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-07T10:06:35.163Z\",\"support\":\"\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":257,\"lat\":\"51.336036\",\"lng\":\"-0.267382\",\"date\":\"2016-06-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Epsom and Ewell\",\"description\":\"This was the day of the referendum result. Me and my mum just finished shopping and was at a stop light in my car waiting for the lights to go, these two young white girls stood on the pavement shouted \\\"Wooo Brexit!\\\" as I drove past them. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Surrey\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-07T12:17:36.782Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-07T15:17:28.876Z\",\"support\":\"No, it all happened too quickly\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":258,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"date\":\"2016-06-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Cleveland Way\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Bethnal Green\",\"description\":\"I am reporting 2 incidents, that took place in the space of 24 hours.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe day before the EU referendum, my mixed-race friend of Chinese \\u0026 Candian heritage, Geni Lou, was scolded on the street with the \\\"Fucking Chink!\\\" in Bethnal Green, while walking home. The next day, my other friend Kieran Warner, of English \\u0026 Jamaican heritage, was harassed by what may seem to be the same woman, when he was at the polling station. The only intelligible part of her rant he understood was her saying \\\"I want things back to the way they used to be.\\\" When Kieran asked \\\"What about human rights \\u0026 woman's rights?\\\", she shouted back \\\"We never had no rights!\\\".\\r\\n\\r\\nThere are potentially more I could report, but when you're on the go \\u0026 in a rush, it's to stop \\u0026 be witness.\\r\\n\\r\\nI was also subject to racial abuse when I was taking a bus back to my temporary abode in Perth, Australia, last December 2015. If you have any information on where I can report this incident, that would be really appreciated. This happens to often \\u0026 I to do something pro-active about it, please.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"e1 4tz\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"East London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Ng, Chin-Yu.\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-07T14:45:32.416Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-07T15:18:12.363Z\",\"support\":\"No one. Just us friends, when we got together.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":259,\"lat\":\"52.531697\",\"lng\":\"0.830378\",\"date\":\"2016-07-07T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Thetford\",\"description\":\"I was called a 'stupid ape' (I'm black) by a woman in a pink Land Rover when I stopped to ask directions back to the main road.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"IP24 1PT\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Norfolk\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-07T19:16:25.324Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-07T21:01:16.220Z\",\"support\":\"I was alone.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":263,\"lat\":\"51.278708\",\"lng\":\"0.521725\",\"date\":\"2003-09-10T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Westerham\",\"description\":\"When I was younger I was told repeatedly to 'fuck off you Nazi' because I am French. Yes, I was totally aware of the pure idiocy of this at the time. The boy repeated it over and over again in class until eventually the teacher told him he was an idiot because Nazi's were from Germany and I am French. As soon as she told him off he turned around and whispered it again. Unfortunately this teacher offered me little comfort when later in the year she said to the class during History 'the English used to hate the French...some things never change' obviously forgetting I was in her class. Although I do not deem these incidents to be severe I dread to think of the rise in racist and xenophobic comments that have been made in schools and other 'bullying' envronments since the referendum, and my heart goes out to them. The accounts of such things have been deeply upsetting on Facebook etc \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Kent\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T14:38:20.662Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T14:38:20.662Z\",\"support\":\"\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":261,\"lat\":\"53.293182\",\"lng\":\"-3.72764\",\"date\":\"2016-03-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"93 Abergele Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Colwyn Bay\",\"description\":\"A woman at a bike shop told me: 'You sound foreign.' I said: 'Yepp.' Then she asked: 'What are you?' Perhaps it's not racist, but I was confused why would she say 'what' instead of 'who', or 'where are you from', or why would she ask at all.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"LL29 7SA\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Conwy\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T14:18:35.400Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:33:28.631Z\",\"support\":\"I was alone. Nobody spoke up.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":262,\"lat\":\"51.58225\",\"lng\":\"-0.39658\",\"date\":\"2016-07-08T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Hillingdon\",\"description\":\"This morning before work, I was indicating to park, a white female sped up in her car going the opposite direction of the car park to try and take the parking space. She was annoyed that I didn't give the space to her (why should I, I was there before her) so waited till I got out the car to say to me, \\\"you people (me being a British Indian) should go back to where you are from! It is people like you who bring this country down!\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T14:35:40.913Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:33:48.531Z\",\"support\":\"A white woman came to ask the woman in the car if everything was okay. She remained relatively silent but seemed to support the woman in the car.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":523,\"lat\":\"54.787715\",\"lng\":\"-6.492315\",\"date\":\"2016-07-23T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Source: Worrying Signs\",\"description\":\"Reporting a witness to Polish flag-burning. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"Vereinigtes Königreich\",\"region\":\"\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Garyspedding\",\"created_at\":\"2016-08-01T14:52:39.257Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-08-01T17:32:44.229Z\",\"support\":\"\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":260,\"lat\":\"51.342817\",\"lng\":\"-0.064421\",\"date\":\"2016-06-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Croydon\",\"description\":\"My Polish neighbour was in our local park with her 2 1/2 year old daughter. They were approached by an older man in his 60's who started shouting abuse at them. \\r\\nHe shouted 'we voted to leave so why the f don't you go home. None of us want you here' \\r\\nThis continued for some time as she gathered her child and left the park. The only other person present was the man's grandson. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T11:47:24.401Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:33:17.197Z\",\"support\":\"No-one else present \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":264,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"date\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Clayfields\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Basildon\",\"description\":\"In Basildon and approached by twenty something man who informed me I needed to return to my country. Then told me I obviously didnt understand a word he was saying 'you foreign f***wit'. Was then informed I should 'f***off' before Im stabbed or chucked out the country.\\r\\n\\r\\nJust to show how stupid this is and how ignorant people are, I am an olive skinned white britain whose family have lived in the UK for over 300 years having emigrated from northern france. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Rick Barber\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T15:11:18.370Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:34:27.528Z\",\"support\":\"No-one around it was 6am\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":265,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"date\":\"2016-07-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Green Dragon Lane\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Brentford\",\"description\":\"Sitting in my car minding my own business waiting to carry out some training for guys working on a site close to Kew Bridge when a young lad approached my car and told me to 'f***off back to my own country, we showed you last week we dont want you here no more'\\r\\n\\r\\nI am an olive skinned white british person whose family have lived in the UK for over 300 years having emigrated here over 300 years ago.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"Rick Barber\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T15:20:35.362Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:35:07.673Z\",\"support\":\"A couple of people passed at the time of the abuse but did nothing and I cannot apportion blame as you never know what might happen.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":266,\"lat\":\"51.903761\",\"lng\":\"-0.196612\",\"date\":\"2016-07-06T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Stevenage\",\"description\":\"A black, heavily accented man working the till in a large supermarket started a conversation with me about how it was now cheaper for tourists to come visit Britain and more expensive for us to travel abroad. A man in the queue behind me interrupted to say \\\"Brexit was the best thing we ever done in the last 5 years.\\\" I think he meant to bully an obvious immigrant who was at work and alone and would hardly have been in a position to argue. I said I couldn't disagree more and said I was an immigrant (I'm American, but not obviously foreign-born). The Brexiteer puffed up his chest and went red in the face and said we should both just go home. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Hertfordshire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-09T09:11:22.546Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-09T11:00:13.102Z\",\"support\":\"I did, but couldn't do much. The man working the till was desperate to smoothe things over because he was at work, and when he shot me anguished looks, I stopped arguing.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":269,\"lat\":\"52.947769\",\"lng\":\"-1.177542\",\"date\":\"2016-07-03T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Hillside\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Nottingham\",\"description\":\"Was waiting for the bus last sunday morning when the british couple beside me started speaking rather loudly about how britain is for british and that they cant even go one day without seeing an immigrant around these days. As if me waiting for the bus with them totally ruined the start of their day. There was no one else there but me so I chose to just keep quiet and ignore it.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Nottinghamshire\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-10T21:26:49.059Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-10T23:09:24.600Z\",\"support\":\"No one else around\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":270,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"date\":\"2016-07-10T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Deansgate\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Manchester\",\"description\":\"I was walking down the street. An Asian guy was in front of me minding his own business when a white Middle Aged man walked into him and forced him against the wall saying move paki, move paki. Leave. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-11T13:17:16.577Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-11T14:26:32.087Z\",\"support\":\"I spoke up and told the guy to go or I'd call the police. He left and I asked the Asian man if he was ok. He said yes, he was used to it and walked off. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":271,\"lat\":\"51.496998\",\"lng\":\"-0.025863\",\"date\":\"2016-07-11T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"At 3.30pm in Tower Hamlets (a predominantly Muslim and Bangladeshi area): the bus is full of children and parents going home when it starts to rain hard against the windows. A parent closes the window... a few seconds later the bus stops and the bus driver comes upstairs. He claims that whoever is making that noise needs to get off or he will not continue to drive the bus. Someone tells him it was someone just shutting a window - he then responds by saying \\\"oh, it better not be bombs or whatever going off up here\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-11T20:00:59.923Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-11T22:01:18.055Z\",\"support\":\"The bus just went incredibly silent, I think we were all a bit confused, but I was incredibly anger afterwards having thought about where that came from.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":272,\"lat\":\"53.390044\",\"lng\":\"-2.59695\",\"date\":\"2016-06-27T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Warrington\",\"description\":\"I was with my parents in an M\\u0026S car park. We've got a Slovenian license plate and people were staring at us (we could see in the rear view mirror). Then someone shouted at us to say we shouldn't be there and should go home. And when we came back to our car someone had thrown litter all over it. My parents told me they'd been shouted at a few times in their car since Brexit. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Warrington\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-11T22:17:29.784Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-11T23:39:55.926Z\",\"support\":\"No one helped. \",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":273,\"lat\":\"50.829432\",\"lng\":\"-0.258855\",\"date\":\"2016-07-11T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"76 Harbour Way\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Shoreham-by-Sea\",\"description\":\"Racist and xenophobic signs forcefully displayed in the window of house opposite the industrial estate in Harbour Way, Shoreham-by-Sea\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"BN43 5HH\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Sussex\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"cr