iday, if you can't handle tourists I suggest you move away yourself\\\"\\\".\\r\\nSeriously so people think this is acceptable?\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\nSource: Worrying signs\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-08-09T10:27:34.936Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-08-09T22:23:41.140Z\",\"support\":\"\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":455,\"lat\":\"51.561948\",\"lng\":\"-0.013139\",\"date\":\"2016-06-29T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Waltham Forest\",\"description\":\"Windshield smashed with crowbar\\r\\nA white male, seemingly in his 40s, was walking in the middle of the road holding what I assumed was a long crowbar and shouting/ ushering me to stop my car. I was with a friend, we slowed down but had no intention to stop once I saw his weapon. AS soon as he got close enough to see our faces he charged at the car. I swerved my car away from him as much as possible and was on the wrong side of the road to avoid him, but somehow he managed to reach and got a full swing into my windshield, managing to piece it fully and sending loads of tiny glass pieces inside the car.\\r\\n\\r\\nI drove down the road, decided to call the police and in the time I had turned around and explained the situation to the police, this man had tried to attack a Somali taxi driver and was shouting expletives specifically regarding Muslims. Fortunately there was a security worker a few cars down who saw the situation and detained him until the police arrived (well done whoever you are) So by the time I had got back, he was on the floor within a minute or two, the police had arrived and took him away.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe’