on!\\\". To my utter amazement, people around us clapped... the guy got up and walked away, red faced. A woman said to me afterwards \\\"I wish I got this on the phone, it was perfect\\\". I wish she did... In few months time, people will indeed be worried about speaking in foreign languages, and then, no one will clap me - they will clap him.\\r\\nSo you see, they actually got their country back.\\r\\nBut, a Luta Continua, of course. We cannot go on self-lacerating. I am not sure what to do in this new country I found myself in. Not yet.It is my second exile, this time I am in exile while being home.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-31T11:14:34.155Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-31T11:14:34.155Z\",\"support\":\"Fellow passengers clapped when the victim of the attack stood up for themselves, one offered verbal support.\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":533,\"lat\":\"51.604175\",\"lng\":\"0.032502\",\"date\":\"2016-07-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Redbridge\",\"description\":\"Second-hand account of men in balaclavas attacking Polish workers with baseball bats. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-08-01T19:44:24.790Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-08-02T05:50:12.350Z\",\"support\":\"\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\"