elf.\\r\\n\\r\\nA woman who was on the tram, who wished to remain anonymous, said: “When I was there I knew it was going to get serious. This kind of incident is really happening. It needs to be noticed we don’t want these kind of incidents happening. The three men got off the tram at Market Street and it stopped there.\\r\\nhttp://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/greater-manchester-news/tram-video-racist-abuse-manchester-11535624#ICID=sharebar_twitter\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":false,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater Manchester\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-08-01T10:57:57.446Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-08-01T10:57:57.446Z\",\"support\":\"Yes\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":499,\"lat\":\"51.878671\",\"lng\":\"-0.420026\",\"date\":\"2016-07-07T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Luton\",\"description\":\"vandalism of Muslim graves today in #Luton with swastikas and \\\"Kill The Muslims\\\" graffiti \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Luton\",\"informant_email\":null,\"informant_name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-08-01T10:53:07.485Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-08-01T11:04:34.220Z\",\"support\":\"\",\"informant_tel\":null,\"informant_permission\":null,\"informant_role\":null,\"type_incident\":null,\"type_incident_other\":null,\"type_location\":null,\"type_location_other\":null,\"reported_to_police\":null,\"approved_at\":null},{\"id\":498,\"lat\":\"51.427871\",\"lng\":\"-0.124058\",\"date\":\"2016-06-28T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Lambeth\",\"description\":\"2 young men in Streatham yelling at Polish man \\u0026 his 